{{Use Indian English|date=October 2015}}
'''Acharya K. K. Chandy''' (1908&ndash;2001) was the President Emeritus, [[Fellowship of Reconciliation]] (India). He was also the founding father of the [[Gurukul]] Ecumenical Center for Peace and also one of the three founder members of Christavashram, [[Kottayam]].

